metadata.name: Her Lips Tasted Like Strawberries
metadata.description:
1/1
1004 x 1260 JPEG

"Vintage Nostalgia" contains retro vintage AI-generated images centered around feelings of sentimentality, liminality, and melancholic desires for things no longer within reach. Through a pastel-colored lens, these artworks depict a romanticized view of the past and the heart-breaking nostalgia that can arise from memories of bygone eras. From retro fashion and vintage kitsch aesthetics, to longing for a future that could be like a forgotten memory, this is what nostalgia feels like to me.
